summary: An Ordinance approving and confirming the assessment and assessment roll of Local Improvement District No. 3189 for the improvement of 9th Avenue Northeast, from East 65th Street to Ravenna Boulevard, all in the City of Seattle, under Ordinance No. 39330, and levying and assessing the amounts thereof against the several lots, tracts, parcels of land and other property as shown on said roll, establishing a Local Improvement Fund.
